page.title: 10Clubs.
page.content: The residents of this area have the oppurtunety to join many local clubs and organizations for the younger members of the community there is Brownies,Guides and Cubs along with an Army Cadet Section.There is also a Majorettes troop as well as a judo Club,Youth Club and Sailing Club.There is also a Womens Institute and Ladies Circle. Among the many charitable organizations there is a branch of the Round Table,the Buffaloes and a Over_41 Club.There are various sports clubs (see Recreation) and entertainment groups (See Entertainment).The Scillonian Club also provides amenities to play snooker,bridge,whist and bingo.
